maneuver.instruction: Drive west on Jalan Lapangan Bola.
Make a right U-turn to stay on Jalan Lapangan Bola.
Turn right onto Jalan Panjang Raya.
Turn left onto Jalan Kebon Jeruk Raya.
Turn left to stay on Jalan Kebon Jeruk Raya.
Turn right onto Jalan Rawa Belong.
Turn left onto Jalan KH. Syahdan.
You have arrived at your destination.

legs.summary: Jalan Kebon Jeruk Raya, Jalan KH. Syahdan
